Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Coal Oil Point
Description: A nature preserve walking distance from campus; watch your step in the tidepools and around the coastal hatchlings!

Name: Jeannine's
Description: The perfect little spot for brunch!

Name: Cristino's Bakery
Description: They have the friendliest staff and the most delicious conchas I've ever had- just writing about them is making me want to drive out and pick up a half dozen.

Name: Camino Pescadero Park
Description: This is my dog's favorite park; there are no trash cans but there's an amazing view of the ocean and benches and tables to boot!

Name: Lizard's Mouth Rock
Description: A fantastic hiking destination! Climbable boulders and rocks galore! But be warned- many inexperienced hikers can get turned around here so just look out for a former boyscout and he'll show you where to go!
